				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Eldrig will be the cause of me going into a mental institute<a name="38410"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">May 5 04 3:36 PM</span></td>
